(159,1,"2019-10-27 01:09:23","2019-10-27 01:09:23","<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Everyone loves a good deal on discount golf clubs, and if you\'re here you no doubt know what is a golf club, but for the sake of being thorough, bear with me on this.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Golf clubs are the tools used to strike the ball when playing golf. In designing a golf club, club makers must take into account ways to maximize the physics of the player\'s swing, while also providing a certain margin for swing error. Hence, the better your swing, the less forgiving a club you need. For a beginner, a club with a more forgiving design is probably best. But, what do we mean by the physics of a player\'s swing, and by more or less forgiving design?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is made of three parts - the Head, the Shaft, and the Grip. ......</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are many types of golf clubs one can choose from, each with their own specs and specific uses.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Drivers</li><li>Fairway Woods</li><li>Hybrids</li><li>Irons &amp; Iron Sets</li><li>Wedges</li><li>Putters</li><li>Complete Sets</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->","Discount Golf Clubs","","inherit","closed","closed","","26-revision-v1","","","2019-10-27 01:09:23","2019-10-27 01:09:23","",26,"http://kad-golf.local//26-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
